name: TBL-Sigil-01
description:
Produced in collaboration with the music artist Contack, this is #01 in a series of The Bad Lament signature virtual reality tunnels and sigils. Each tunnel has been hand painted in VR and features a representative sigal marking the significance of these single edition works. 4K version available for the collector. 

TBL-Sigil-01  manifests prosperity.
